## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the subjective nature of the topic. The fear of death is deeply personal and can vary widely among individuals based on cultural, religious, and personal beliefs. Additionally, the sources used may not cover all possible perspectives or recent developments in the understanding of death anxiety.